<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="org71026d0">Custom Encrypted Fields</h3>



<p>Password. Username. URL. Not enough?<br>Create your custom encrypted fields.<br>Rule entropy. See through the chaos. Let order win.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="org633773d">Automatic Database Opening</h3>



<p>Create an&nbsp;<code>AutoOpen</code>&nbsp;group to open databases automatically.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><code>Username</code> field – path to keyfile (optional)</li>



<li><code>Password</code> field – database password</li>



<li><code>URL</code> field – full path to the target <code>.kdbx</code></li>
</ul>



