<p>KeepassXC secures your secrets.<br>DeadSwitch&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/DeadSwitch404/vault-crypt">Vault-Crypt</a>&nbsp;protects your .kdbx files.<br>Layered security is not paranoia. It&#8217;s thinking in advance.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="orgd4a5390">Ghost Rule: Secrets Stay Where The Signal Dies</h2>



